summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from H. F. Hancher, and Jennie G. Hancher, his wife, George E. Large and Helena C. Large, his wife, and M. B. Archer and Arabella Archer his wife, to the City of Seattle, dated February 1st, in the year of our Lord Nineteen Hundred Eleven (1911) all that certain tract, lot or parcel of land situated in the County of King, State of Washington.
